title: HALF PAST DEAD 2002 IN H.264-MULTI AUDIO BY WINKER
description:
When Alcatraz re-opens, the first inmate scheduled for the electric chair has vital information on the whereabouts of the proceeds of his last crime. Unwilling to let this fotune go up in smoke, a criminal commando (Chestnut) infiltrates the prison to find out where the $200 million stash of gold is hidden. However, an undercover FBI agent (Seagal) becomes the "fly-in-the-ointment" of this would-be raid...
